ActFarm Products Agencies Act
SubjectAmend the Canadian Hatching Egg Producers Grant of Authority
PrecisOrder amending the CANADIAN HATCHING EGG PRODUCERS GRANT OF AUTHORITY in order to remove the definitions of Agency, broiler hatching egg, chick, commodity board, marketing and signatory provinces; amend the definitions of Regulations and provincial quota; and renumber certain sections to improve clarity.
